    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>hoisin sauce</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can’t handle the heat? Go easy!)<strong> fish sauce, </strong>1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tbsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span><strong> water</strong></p><p>Cook for 2-3 min or until the sauce begins to reduce and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
