    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a separate large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-low heat</p><p>Once hot, crack your<strong> egg[s]</strong> into the pan and cook, covered, for 2 min or until done to your liking – this is your<strong> fried egg[s]</strong></p>",
