      "instruction": "<p>Once done, remove the pan from the heat</p><p>Pick your <strong>basil leaves</strong> from their stalks, discard the stalks</p><p>Add the<strong> basil leaves</strong> to the chicken and give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> fragrant Thai-style chicken stir-fry</strong></p>",
